A vintage 1970s Japanese toy advertisement style illustration showing colorful spinning tops in dynamic motion on a circular arena, with dramatic speed lines radiating outward. The tops feature intricate mechanical details with layered metal rings and attack points, captured mid-collision with sparks flying. The scene is viewed from a low angle looking up, giving the spinning tops an epic, heroic presence. Warm nostalgic color palette with faded yellows, bold reds, and metallic silvers. Soft grain texture overlay and slightly desaturated tones evoke retro anime merchandise catalogs. Small scattered mechanical parts and assembly pieces frame the edges of the composition.
